  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\n\r\nUX could be improved by merging functionality of `--nodekey-path` with the `--nodekey`  argument. (https://github.com/ethereum/py-evm/pull/1424#discussion_r227424899)\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n\r\nWe should be able to merge the functionality of `--nodekey-path` with the `--nodekey` argument and just do detection on whether the arg is referencing a file or that it's just a string nodekey.\r\n",
